Ven pongal

Qty.
 - Moong dal (1/2 cup)
 - Rice (1/2 cup) 
 - Black peppercorns

Instructions.
1. Fry cumin seeds in ghee. Once they have popped, add the rice and moong dal. Fry these until they become dry.

2. Add 3 cups of water, as well as a handful of black peppercorns and salt.

3. Cook this in a pressure cooker (in an instant pot, for six minutes).
